## Hermes-Trading System

The AI trading system runs on Railway. Key facts:
- **Scripts:** `/app/Hermes-Trading/scripts/`
- **DB:** `/hermes-data/trading.db` (WAL mode, on Railway Volume)
- **Profile:** `/root/.hermes/profiles/trading/` (Alpaca keys via Railway env vars: `ALPACA_API_KEY`, `ALPACA_SECRET_KEY`)
- **Kill switch:** `/hermes-data/KILL_SWITCH` (touch to halt)
- **Cron jobs:** Premarket Scan, Intraday Scan, Monitor, Daily Recap, Weekly Review, Monthly Review, Kanban Watcher (all 8 run on Railway)
- **Concurrency limit:** Max 2 kanban tasks dispatched simultaneously

## Coding Project Rules

- **All work goes through kanban** for projects with boards. No direct work outside the board.
- **Code lives at `/app/<project>/`** in the Railway container.
- **coding-project-lifecycle skill** governs the correct workflow. Load it before starting any coding project work.

## Memory Hygiene

- MEMORY.md: behavioral rules, tool quirks, system config only. Max 2,200 chars.
- USER.md: user preferences only. Max 1,375 chars.
- Project details → `/root/.hermes/projects/info/` files (unlimited size)
- Project state → vault `project-state.md` files
- Session outcomes → hindsight memory bank (auto-retained every 5 turns)

## Profiles

Each profile lives at `/root/.hermes/profiles/<name>/` with its own `AGENTS.md` (and optionally `SOUL.md`, `models.json`).

| Profile | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| `agy-lane` | Agent lane for autonomous coding |
| `backend-eng` | Backend engineering agent |
| `claude-lane` | Claude Code delegation lane |
| `frontend-eng` | Frontend engineering agent |
| `ops` | Operations agent |
| `pm` | Project management agent |
| `researcher` | Research agent |
| `reviewer` | Code review agent |
| `writer` | Writing agent |
| `analyst` | Analysis agent |
| `mimirs-will` | General agent |

**Cron jobs:** Set `profile: "<name>"` on cron jobs to run them under a specific profile.

## Railway-Specific Notes

- **Volume:** `/hermes-data/` is the persistent Railway Volume. All data that must survive restarts lives here.
- **Wiki vault:** `/app/wiki/` — cloned from GitHub (Encephalon-Mageia). Sync via wiki-git-sync.sh cron job.
- **Logs:** `/hermes-data/logs/` — check these first when debugging.
- **Tailscale:** Running in userspace mode. SSH via `tailscale set --ssh`. IP available via `tailscale ip -4`.
- **Health check:** Port 8080 responds with HTTP 200. Required by Railway for deployment validation.
- **Dashboard:** `hermes-web-ui start --port 8648`
